`8Keywords``   : Poison
`8Categories`` : 
`4++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++``

All Nyissans have the ability to prepare poison from different herbs and
plants. They can envenom their weapons, making them far more lethal than they
look, or put it in the poor victim's food.

